				id: "4B57E1D945082425"
				title: "Где тяжело дышать (RU)"
				type: "custom"
			}]
			x: -1.8d
			y: 9.6d
		}
		{
			description: [
				"Air isn't the same everywhere in this mod:"
				""
				"HIGH IN THE MOUNTAINS AND DEEP UNDERGROUND the air gets thin -"
				"breathing gets harder and your air supply slowly drains. A"
				"Respirator protects you here."
				""
				"IN THE NETHER AND IN THE DEEPEST, MOST DANGEROUS SPOTS there"
				"may be no air at all - a Respirator won't be enough there, you"
				"need something stronger: a Bottle of Soulfire as a last resort,"
				"or a Potion of Free Breathing (a renamed Water Breathing potion)"
				"- it protects you from lack of air absolutely everywhere, no"
				"exceptions."
				""
				"NEAR SOUL FIRE your air neither gets worse nor better - it just"
				"holds steady wherever it currently is. An Air Bladder is"
				"useless here (there's nothing to top up), but if your air is"
				"already running out, Soul Fire at least keeps it from hitting"
				"zero."
				""
				"The exact heights and places where breathing gets hard depend"
				"on this pack's own settings - in one pack it might be deep"
				"caves, in another it's above a certain mountain height. Trust"
				"your own feel for it, and use the Safety Lantern as a visual"
				"indicator."
			]
			id: "6D637490054BCFCA"
			rewards: [
				{
					id: "7DFF000000000143"
					type: "xp"
					xp: 30
				}
				{
