		}
		{
			description: [
				"Besides height and depth, specific nearby blocks also affect"
				"the air around you:"
				""
				"FIRE AND LAVA - the air near them turns bad fast, as if the"
				"flames are burning up all the oxygen around them."
				""
				"SOUL FIRE, SOUL TORCHES AND SOUL LANTERNS - the air near them"
				"doesn't improve, but it doesn't run out either, it just holds"
				"steady (see the previous quest)."
				""
				"PORTALS (End Portal, Nether Portal, End Gateway) -"
				"surprisingly, the air right next to them is always clean and"
				"fresh, no matter what's going on around them."
				""
				"These blocks override the general air of the area: even if"
				"you're already gasping deep in a cave, stepping right up to a"
				"portal will let you catch a full breath immediately."
			]
			id: "65ADB097AD094D9A"
